---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IELTS Writing Lab"
  description="雅思写作底层能力练习：逐句拆解、回译训练与 AI 分析检查。"
>
  <section class="writing-lab" data-writing-lab>
    <div class="lab-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">IELTS Writing Lab</p>
      <h1>SRT Console</h1>
      <p>
        Sentence Reverse Translation Console. 粘贴一篇英文范文，先拆成中文句子，
        再逐句翻回英文。最后用 AI 对照原文、你的表达和建议版本，沉淀语法、
        表达、chunk 与句型。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lab-panel input-panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div>
          <span class="step">01</span>
          <h2>粘贴范文</h2>
        </div>
        <button class="ghost-button" type="button" data-load-example>载入示例</button>
      </div>
      <textarea
        data-source-text
        rows="9"
        placeholder="在这里粘贴任意英文文章或雅思范文..."
      ></textarea>
      <div class="action-row">
        <p data-source-meta>等待输入文章</p>
        <button class="primary-button" type="button" data-split-text>AI 拆解为中文</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lab-panel sentence-panel" hidden data-practice-panel>
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div>
          <span class="step">02</span>
          <h2>根据中文逐句回译</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="status-pill" data-sentence-count>0 句</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sentence-list" data-sentence-list></div>
      <div class="check-bar">
        <div>
          <strong>完成后进行检查</strong>
          <p>选择要检查的句子序号，分析结果会出现在对应句子下面；不满意时可重新选择同一句再分析。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="analysis-control">
          <span>选择句子</span>
          <div class="sentence-picker" data-analysis-targets></div>
          <small>一次只能选择一句；点击序号会定位到对应句子。</small>
          <button class="primary-button" type="button" data-analyze>AI 分析所选句子</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .writing-lab {
      padding: 58px 0 88px;
    }

    .lab-hero {
      max-width: 760px;
      padding-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .lab-hero h1 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 64px);
    }

    .lab-hero p {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .lab-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 90%, transparent);
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .lab-panel + .lab-panel {
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .panel-head,
    .action-row,
    .check-bar,
    .analysis-row,
    .analysis-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .panel-head {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .panel-head h2 {
      margin: 4px 0 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .step,
    .status-pill,
    .analysis-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      padding: 0 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 750;
    }

    textarea,
    .answer-input {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      outline: none;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .answer-box {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-soft) 56%, transparent),
          var(--surface) 34%
        );
      padding: 12px;
      transition:
        border-color 160ms ease,
        box-shadow 160ms ease,
        background 160ms ease;
    }

    .answer-box:focus-within {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--surface);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 14%, transparent);
    }

    .answer-box-head,
    .answer-box-foot {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 0 2px;
    }

    .answer-box-head {
      margin-bottom: 9px;
    }

    .answer-box-head span {
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .answer-box-head small,
    .answer-box-foot {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 650;
    }

    .answer-box-foot {
      justify-content: flex-end;
      margin-top: 8px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .answer-box .answer-input {
      display: block;
      min-height: 118px;
      border-color: transparent;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 92%, transparent);
      padding: 15px 16px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 76%, transparent);
    }

    .answer-box .answer-input::placeholder {
      color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--muted) 70%, transparent);
    }

    .answer-box .answer-input:focus {
      border-color: transparent;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent),
        0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 14%, transparent);
    }

    textarea:focus,
    .answer-input:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 18%, transparent);
    }

    .action-row {
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .action-row p,
    .check-bar p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .primary-button,
    .ghost-button {
      min-height: 44px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .primary-button {
      border: 0;
      background: var(--text);
      color: var(--bg);
    }

    .ghost-button {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .sentence-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .sentence-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .sentence-card header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .sentence-number {
      display: grid;
      flex: 0 0 34px;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--text);
      color: var(--bg);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .chinese-line {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 750;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .answer-input {
      min-height: 92px;
    }

    .check-bar {
      position: sticky;
      bottom: 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 96%, transparent);
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .check-bar strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .analysis-control {
      display: grid;
      min-width: min(100%, 310px);
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .analysis-control span,
    .analysis-control small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 750;
    }

    .sentence-picker {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      max-width: 360px;
    }

    .sentence-picker button {
      display: grid;
      position: relative;
      min-width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      place-items: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-soft) 70%, transparent),
          var(--surface)
        );
      color: var(--text);
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 850;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition:
        transform 160ms ease,
        border-color 160ms ease,
        box-shadow 160ms ease,
        background 160ms ease,
        color 160ms ease;
    }

    .sentence-picker button:hover,
    .sentence-picker button:focus-visible {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 18%, transparent);
    }

    .sentence-picker button.is-selected {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background:
        linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 24%, var(--text)),
          var(--text)
        );
      color: var(--bg);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 20%, transparent),
        0 10px 22px color-mix(in srgb, var(--text) 14%, transparent);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .sentence-picker button.is-selected::after {
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      top: -7px;
      right: -7px;
      display: grid;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      place-items: center;
      border: 2px solid var(--surface);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .sentence-picker button span {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .analysis-box {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 16px;
    }

    .analysis-section {
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .analysis-section h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .analysis-section p,
    .analysis-section li {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .analysis-section p,
    .analysis-section ul {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .analysis-section ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .compare-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .compare-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .compare-item span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .compare-item p {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .error-message {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, #d33 42%, var(--line));
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, #d33 8%, var(--surface));
      padding: 10px 12px;
      color: #b42318;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .writing-lab {
        padding-top: 36px;
      }

      .lab-panel {
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .panel-head,
      .action-row,
      .check-bar {
        align-items: stretch;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .primary-button,
      .ghost-button {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .compare-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

